🚫 DON’T Do This:
js
Copy
Edit
import app from "#app.js";              // ❌ wrong
import usersRouter from "#api/users.js"; // ❌ wrong
Even though those files are named .js, your package.json is expecting you to import them without that extension. That's how imports map works in Node 22.

